No issues found. Let me commit and push the fix:

Progress update: Fix CI: disable uv cache pruning in copilot-setup-steps.yml

The astral-sh/setup-uv@v5 post step runs 'uv cache prune --ci' which
consistently times out after 5 minutes (exit code 2), causing all
Copilot agent PR runs to fail. Since this is a transient CI environment
with no cache persistence, pruning serves no purpose. Setting
prune-cache: false disables the problematic post step.

